# vastai_volume (Resource)

Manages a Vast.ai local volume. Volumes provide persistent storage that can be attached to instances. Volumes are created from volume offers (use the `vastai_volume_offers` data source) or cloned from existing volumes. Marketplace listing/unlisting is supported.

